data.description: This home qualifies for a $15K GRANT! Grant DOESN'T require repayment & can be used towards CLOSING COSTS, REDUCE interest rate or to REDUCE the balance of the loan. This McNeil Farms home has 5 BEDROOMS on the 2nd floor along with 2 full BATHS. All bedrooms are ample size and the primary bedroom is HUGE. The first floor offers a LARGE family room, dining room, FLEX SPACE, laundry room & 1/2 bath. Exit through the sliding doors onto a HUGE deck and PAVER PATIO with built-in firepit. Yard is FENCED too. Basement is unfinished but can be turned into add'l living space & is plumbed for ANOTHER BATH. And, the SOLAR PANELS on the roof  provide IMMEDIATE savings on ELECTRIC bills.
